## ⚠️ Important Disclaimers

**This tool does NOT provide:**
- Legal advice or case strategy
- Diagnostic conclusions
- Filing guidance or motion recommendations
- Professional judgment substitution

**This tool is NOT:**
- A replacement for legal counsel
- A clinical assessment tool
- An authoritative voice on custody matters

**All outputs require professional review.** This tool helps organize and translate documentation—it does not evaluate cases or make recommendations.

## How It Works

1. **Fact Extraction** — Separates factual statements from emotional language
2. **Pattern Mapping** — Maps facts to predefined child-impact pattern categories
3. **Relevance Analysis** — Weighs patterns across attorney/GAL/clinician perspectives
4. **Output Generation** — Produces audience-appropriate summaries

See [docs/DEVLOG.md](docs/DEVLOG.md) for detailed development decisions.

## Built With

- [Kiro CLI](https://kiro.dev) — AI-powered development workflows
- Python / Flask — Local web interface

